text: Parvana Mirzaguliyeva (; born 15 April 1988) is an Azerbaijani former footballer who played as a defender. She has been a member of the Azerbaijan women's national team since 2010. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers
